1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T16:12:15.000Z","msg":"我錯,睇返原來係戴卓爾夫人跌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T03:22:10.000Z","msg":"經典野都可以記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6100af8cd548a211563196566fa3199910a01e","tid":2142783,"uid":191926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T03:29:05.000Z","msg":"想講好耐<br />\n主因之一係美國當時玩接觸政策<br />\n<br />\n仲有<br />\n好多人講的保留港島，九龍半島 <br />\n英國係諗過 但完全無執行性 好快就放棄<br />\n(就算依家都係難以執行)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PwvkQWU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPwvkQWU.png&h=2d0e0484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你只要看下南京，北京條約就明<br />\n<br />\n80年代的新界包括<br />\n<br />\n機場<br />\n貨櫃碼頭<br />\n堆田區<br />\n工業區<br />\n大部份發電廠<br />\n大部份淡水湖<br />\n好多公司總部(倒無線，亞視總部)<br />\n大部份大學學院(除左港大，理工)<br />\n<br />\n無左新界 <br />\n根本無可能安置咁多人，機構去港島<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有大嶼山，長洲，南牙島，蒲台島，東龍洲都唔係南北京條約的範圍<br />\n<br />\n香港會面臨內陸化的嚴重問題"},{"pid":"f6777a07f1ed98e8271aeeaa3f608216f85bc1eb","tid":2142783,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T03:59:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a26600ea025ab02a99258cba84aef8d1b813b3cf","tid":2142783,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:00:27.000Z","msg":"大中華膠、司徒老X當道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c522c2b6f980a0092d4476f5aec01a320363f6f5","tid":2142783,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:04:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f3bf8680a105e73a8e3e0d6f48ba62f24ce53c67","tid":2142783,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e2bbb4ace9becf15bf2d38b012735faa0b3ce64","tid":2142783,"uid":253608,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"29397863b863680980ac3d51cc5106a5fa45f7f1","tid":2142783,"uid":5218,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score